text: Kentucky - The Hillary Clinton for President Campaign today announced it will host an Election Watch Party on Tuesday, April 22nd. Hillary volunteers and staffers will come together to watch Pennsylvania's results come in. What: Election Watch Party  When:Tuesday, April 22, 2008, 7:30 p.m.  Where: 1357 Bardstown RoadLouisville, Kentucky 40204
title: Press Release - Clinton Campaign to Host Election Watch Party in Louisville
